\left | \sum_{i=1}^{2^r}x_i \right | \leq 2^r \max |x_i|.
\begin{eqnarray}|x+y|^n &=& \left |\sum_{i=0}^n {n \choose i}x^iy^{n-i} \right| \\ &\leq & 2(n+1)\max_{0 \leq i \leq n} \left |{n \choose i}x^iy^{n-i}\right | \\&\leq &4(n+1)(|x|+|y|)^n\end{eqnarray}.
